**Priestess** | Townsfolk Power | Temporary
__Basics__
Each night, the Priestess can attempt to remove a curse from a player.
__Details__
Each Night, the Priestess can select a player. If that player has been cursed, it is removed and the Priestess is informed.
If the player is a cursed civilian they will be turned into a citizen.
Selecting a player is an immediate action.
The curse caster who applied the curse will also be informed it was removed, but not from which player.
The Priestesses is immune to the effects of curse but can still have the effect.

__Simplified__
The Priestess is a townsfolk role who can remove a curse during the night.
If a curse is removed, both the Priestess and the Curse Caster are informed, however the Curse Caster is not informed who it was removed from.
